article.description: — Ricky Council IV had 20 points as Wichita State beat East Carolina 70-62 on Saturday.
article.headline: Council IV lifts Wichita St. over East Carolina 70-62
article.linkText: Council IV lifts Wichita St. over East Carolina 70-62
article.story: WICHITA, Kan. -- — Ricky Council IV had 20 points as Wichita State beat East Carolina 70-62 on Saturday. Craig Porter Jr. had 15 points and 10 rebounds for Wichita State (15-12, 6-9 American Athletic Conference). Tyson Etienne added 12 points. Morris Udeze had 12 points. Tristen Newton had 16 points, 11 rebounds and six assists for the Pirates (15-14, 6-11). Vance Jackson added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
